#| "today and all the threads that have been active today."
msgid ""
"This view uses day-by-day groups. Messages are threaded. So for example, in "
"<quote>Today</quote> you will find all the messages that arrived today and "
"all the threads that have been active today. Uses the same grouping as "
"Activity by Date, Flat."
msgstr ""
"Cet affichage utilise des regroupements de dates intelligemment définis. Les "
"messages ne sont pas assemblés par fil de discussion. Par exemple, dans "
"<quote>Aujourd'hui</quote>, vous trouverez tous les messages arrivés "
"aujourd'hui et tout les flux qui ont été actifs aujourd'hui."

#. Tag: term
#: configure.docbook:1138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current Activity, Flat"
msgstr "Activité actuelle, liste simple"

#. Tag: para
#: configure.docbook:1139
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This view uses smart date range groups. Messages are threaded. So for "
